quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,"Ruin is for every open slanderer, backbiter."
  104,2,"Who accumulated wealth and hoarded it, counting."
  104,3,"Does he think that his wealth will prolong his stay on earth forever?"
  104,4,"Never! He will certainly be thrown into the Crushing One."
  104,5,"And what have you understood what the Crushing One is!"
  104,6,"The fire of Allah, that is ablaze."
  104,7,"Which will climb on to the hearts."
  104,8,"Indeed it will be shut over them."
  104,9,"In extended columns."
